name: evan hall
date: 2022-11-05
purpose: program to query hearthstone cards

routes (GET):
"/cards": returns all the cards
"/cards?": returns a query of the cards
"/cards/:id": returns the card data

dependacies: 
http
pug
path
node:querystring


run instuctions:
node server.js
ensure the following files share a directory with the server.js on execution
card.pug
cards.pug
cards.json

queries:
"name": queries for all cards with a name containing the given substring
"class": queries for all cards with the given class
"limit": limits the amound of results returned to the given number
